â†’ â€œDuring Greed days, allow frequent, consistentâ€‘winner traders to increase position size and trade frequency, but monitor drawdowns.â€

Optional bonuses
Predictive model in src/model.py: nextâ€‘day PnL bucket classifier using sentiment + behavior features.

